表格订单详情的约束名称

TK_ORDER_DETAILINFO


表格订单详情的服务器检验表达式

表格订单详情的代码预览

drop table if exists ORDER_DETAILINFO;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: ORDER_DETAILINFO */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ORDER_DETAILINFO
(
ORDER_ID varchar(12) not null,
MARITAL_STATUS char(1),
EDUCATIONAL_STATUS char(2),
VOCATION_STATUS char(1),
COMM_ADDR_PROVINCE int(6),
COMM_ADDR_CITY int(6),
COMM_ADDR_DISTRICT int(6),
COMM_ADDR varchar(128),
CONTACT_NAME varchar(256),
CONTACT_PHONE char(11),
DEPOSIT_AMOUNT decimal(10,2),
COMPANY_CHANNEL_ID int,
COMPANY_CHANNEL_NAME varchar(256),
COMPANY_CHANNEL_PHONE char(11),
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (ORDER_ID)
);
